  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.hazelcast.nio.serialization.DataSerializable, AclfGen, NameTag, OpfGen, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.InternalEObject

    public class OpfGenImpl
extends AclfGenImpl
implements OpfGen
    An implementation of the model object 'Base Opf Gen'.

    The following features are implemented:

    • Operating Mode
    • Coeff A
    • Coeff B
    • Fixed Cost
    • Inc Cost
    • Opf Limits
    • Capacity Limit
